snippet.textDisplay:
People complaining about this being like Bollywood, you guys don't seem to have any clue about Pakistani Music. It's nothing like Bollywood. People who follow Pakistani music to heart know that underground bands of late 90s and many in the past 10-15 years tend to have many of such melodious slow tracks. Coke studio can't just keep playing the same folk/sufi/qawali stuff, and neither should you fuss about a different type of soulful tune. 

This Ali Khan's version is a brilliant addition. Absolutely love it!!!!!!!!!!!!!
snippet.textOriginal:
